      <div class="container position-relative">
        <h1>About</h1>
        <p>Where every Cebu Journey becomes story.</p>
        <nav class="breadcrumbs">
          <ol>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li class="current">About</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div><!-- End Page Title -->
    <!-- Travel About Section -->
    <section id="travel-about" class="travel-about section">

      <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center mb-5">
            <div class="intro-content" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
              <h2>More Than Just a Trip</h2>
              <p class="lead">Explore Cebu in a fresh, effortless way. From hidden scenic spots to local cultural experiences, every journey is designed to be enriching, memorable, and full of moments you’ll truly enjoy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
          <div class="col-lg-5" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="300">
            <div class="hero-image">
              <img src="../../assets/dot/sinulog.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="Travel Adventure">
                <div class="experience-badge" data-aos="slide-right" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <img src="../../assets/dot/lovetheph.png" class="img-fluid" alt="Travel Adventure">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-1" data-aos="slide-left" data-aos-delay="400">
            <div class="story-content">
              <div class="story-badge">
                <i class="bi bi-compass"></i>
                <span>Our Story</span>
              </div>
              <h3>Where Discovery Begins</h3>
              <p>It all started with Seiha Global Academy’s optional tours. As these trips became a regular part of our study-abroad programs, an idea began to take shape. Why not create a dedicated travel service? We wanted to offer more than just sightseeing, crafting journeys that are seamless, fun, and full of discovery for every traveler.</p>
              <p>Over time, our trips grew beyond Japanese students. Today, we design experiences for anyone curious about Cebu, combining local culture, scenic escapes, and unforgettable moments. Every journey is thoughtfully planned so travelers can focus on exploring, connecting, and making memories that last a lifetime.</p>

              <div class="mission-box">
                <div class="mission-icon">
                  <i class="bi bi-globe-americas"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="mission-text">
                  <h4>Our Vision</h4>
                  <p>"To shape a globally connected and compassionate future through impactful educational travel."</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div class="features-grid" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
