                <h3>What Makes Us Different</h3>
              </div>

              <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                  <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-front">
                      <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fa-regular fa-handshake"></i>
                      </div>
                      <h4>Trusted Local Partners</h4>
                      <p>We collaborate with top hotels and resorts in Cebu to ensure smooth, quality stays.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-back">
                      <p>We collaborate with top hotels and resorts in Cebu to ensure smooth, comfortable, and high-quality stays for our clients. Through our trusted partnerships, we are able to offer reliable accommodations, excellent service standards, and seamless travel experiences—so every guest can relax and enjoy Cebu with confidence and convenience.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                  <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-front">
                      <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-leanpub"></i>
                      </div>
                      <h4>Immersive Learning</h4>
                      <p>Our English programs combine proven methods with real-life experiences for effective learning.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-back">
                      <p>Our English programs combine proven teaching methods with real-life experiences to help students build strong communication skills. Through interactive lessons, practical exercises, and everyday conversation practice, learners gain confidence, improve fluency, and use English naturally in real-world situations.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
                  <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-front">
                      <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-person-chalkboard"></i>
                      </div>
                      <h4>Experienced Teachers</h4>
                      <p>Native and local instructors guide students with expertise, support, and care.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-back">
                      <p>Native and local instructors guide students with expertise, dedication, and care. With strong teaching experience and cultural understanding, they provide personalized support that helps learners grow confidently, improve faster, and achieve their language goals.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                  <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-front">
                      <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-church"></i>
                      </div>
                      <h4>Cultural Experiences</h4>
                      <p> We integrate local culture, activities, and excursions into every journey.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-back">
                      <p>We integrate local culture, activities, and excursions into every journey to give students meaningful, real-world experiences. By exploring communities, traditions, and destinations firsthand, learners gain deeper understanding, confidence, and lasting memories beyond the classroom.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                  <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-front">
                      <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fa-regular fa-calendar-days"></i>
                      </div>
                      <h4>Flexible Programs</h4>
                      <p>Online or face-to-face, our programs adapt to your schedule and goals.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-back">
                      <p>Whether online or face-to-face, our programs are designed to adapt to your schedule and personal goals. We provide flexible learning options that allow you to study at your own pace while receiving quality instruction and support.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
                  <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-front">
                      <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-route"></i>
                      </div>
                      <h4>Seamless Travel & Learning</h4>
                      <p> We design every experience to be effortless, enriching, and memorable.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-back">
                      <p>We thoughtfully design every experience to be effortless, enriching, and truly memorable, ensuring comfort, growth, and lasting value for every participant.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-5">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div class="journey-timeline" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
              <div class="timeline-header text-center mb-5">
                <h3>What Shaped Us</h3>
                <p> From humble beginnings in Japan to global classrooms and curated journeys in Cebu, our story is one of growth, passion, and connection.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-container">
                <div class="timeline-track"></div>

                <div class="timeline-milestone" data-aos="slide-right" data-aos-delay="300">
                  <div class="milestone-marker" style="background: #20a04a;">
                    <span class="year">1985</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="milestone-content">
                    <h4>SEIHA English Academy</h4>
                    <p>Founded by CEO Masami Sakaguchi in western Japan, SEIHA English Academy focused on children aged 3 months to 14 years, with classes co-taught by native English and Japanese teachers using Total Physical Response.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-milestone" data-aos="slide-left" data-aos-delay="400">
                  <div class="milestone-marker" style="background: #36c6f4;">
                    <span class="year">2015</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="milestone-content">
                    <h4>UPTALK Seiha</h4>
                    <p>Seiha English Network Philippines Inc., or UPTALK Seiha, was established to offer online English classes for students in Japan. Filipino and Japanese teachers apply the Seiha Method from the Cebu-based office.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-milestone" data-aos="slide-right" data-aos-delay="500">
                  <div class="milestone-marker" style="background: #f15a28;">
                    <span class="year">2019</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="milestone-content">
                    <h4>Seiha Global Academy</h4>
                    <p>To meet growing demand from foreign visitors, Seiha Global Academy opened in Cebu, offering face-to-face English classes and excursions. SEIHA continues to pursue global growth.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-milestone" data-aos="slide-left" data-aos-delay="600">
                  <div class="milestone-marker" style="background: #f79421;">
                    <span class="year">2025</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="milestone-content">
                    <h4>Seiha World Travel</h4>
                    <p>SWT was launched to create meaningful journeys in Cebu, blending exploration, culture, and learning for students and visitors alike. True to its values, SEIHA continues evolving to connect language, culture, and experiences worldwide.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
